      "zh": "虽然绝缘胶带主要用来给电线绝缘，但这个东西的用武之地能被聪明人无限放大。例如一些简单的维护，将散件进行拼凑，捆绑物品，对握把进行包裹从而起到防滑作用等。",
      "en": "Although insulating tape is primarily intended for insulation of wires, its practical application is limited only by the creativity of its owner. Most typical cases include minor maintenance, holding together split parts, binding some stuff together and anti-slip wrapping of handles."
